com.thomsonreuters.upa.perftools.upajconsperf

Class ConsumerThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thomsonreuters.upa.perftools.upajconsperf.ConsumerThread
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResponseCallback, java.lang.Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConsumerThreadReactor

    public class ConsumerThread
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable, ResponseCallback
    Provides the logic that consumer connections use in upajConsPerf for connecting to a provider, requesting items, and processing the received refreshes and updates.
